abstract: A disappointing outlook from Cisco Systems rattled the market, as did a report that inflation rose in China in October at its fastest pace in more than two years.
snippet: A disappointing outlook from Cisco Systems rattled the market, as did a report that inflation rose in China in October at its fastest pace in more than two years.
lead_paragraph: Stocks fell Thursday, dragged down mostly by the technology sector as it reacted to a disappointing earnings forecast from Cisco Systems.

headline.main: Wall Street Falls After Cisco Trims Its Outlook
headline.print_headline: Wall Street Falls After Cisco Trims Its Outlook
